  <entry>
    <title>使用Hexo + GitHub Pages搭建个人博客站点</title>
    <url>/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo-GitHub-Pages%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="环境安装" class="heading-control"><a href="#环境安装" class="headerlink" title="环境安装"></a>环境安装<a class="heading-anchor" href="#环境安装" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><ul>
<li>Node</li>
<li>Git</li>
<li>Hexo</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="初始化" class="heading-control"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化<a class="heading-anchor" href="#初始化" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="主题安装" class="heading-control"><a href="#主题安装" class="headerlink" title="主题安装"></a>主题安装<a class="heading-anchor" href="#主题安装" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><ul>
<li>安装<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">NexT主题<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span></li>
</ul>
<h1 id="配置" class="heading-control"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置<a class="heading-anchor" href="#配置" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><ul>
<li>主站配置（hexo/_config.yml）</li>
<li>主题配置（hexo/themes/next/_config.yml）<ul>
<li>配置reminder</li>
<li>配置footer</li>
<li>配置Creative Commons 4.0 International License</li>
<li>配置Scheme</li>
<li>配置menu：新建about/tags/categories各自对应的page，修改各自的index.md文件，修改配置文件</li>
<li>配置sidebar、avatar、social、social_icons</li>
<li>配置symbols_count_time</li>
<li>配置reward</li>
<li>配置mobile_layout_economy</li>
<li>配置codeblock</li>
<li>配置reading_progress</li>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9ob3hpcy5naXRodWIuaW8vSGV4bytOZXh0JTIwU0VPJUU0JUJDJTk4JUU1JThDJTk2Lmh0bWw=" title="https://hoxis.github.io/Hexo+Next%20SEO%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96.html">配置SEO<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>：HTML元标记中的content直接添加至_config.yml对应位置即可，无需添加至head.swig</li>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cDovL2plZmZ5YW5nLnRvcC9IZXhvL0hleG8lRTQlQjglQkIlRTklQTIlOThOZXh0JUU3JUJFJThFJUU1JThDJTk2Lw==" title="http://jeffyang.top/Hexo/Hexo%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98Next%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/">修改文章内链接的样式<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>：最新版本中添加位置为<code>hexo/themes/next/source/css/main.styl</code></li>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuamlhbnNodS5jb20vcC9mNDY1OGRmNjZhMTU=" title="https://www.jianshu.com/p/f4658df66a15">配置valine评论系统<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span></li>
<li>配置标题锚点</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="新建文章" class="heading-control"><a href="#新建文章" class="headerlink" title="新建文章"></a>新建文章<a class="heading-anchor" href="#新建文章" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new [layout] <span class="string">"postName"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="生成静态页面" class="heading-control"><a href="#生成静态页面" class="headerlink" title="生成静态页面"></a>生成静态页面<a class="heading-anchor" href="#生成静态页面" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="本地启动" class="heading-control"><a href="#本地启动" class="headerlink" title="本地启动"></a>本地启动<a class="heading-anchor" href="#本地启动" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="部署到GitHub-Pages" class="heading-control"><a href="#部署到GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="部署到GitHub Pages"></a>部署到GitHub Pages<a class="heading-anchor" href="#部署到GitHub-Pages" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><ul>
<li>申请GitHub账号并进行配置</li>
<li>配置GitHub Pages</li>
<li>部署<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="参考" class="heading-control"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考<a class="heading-anchor" href="#参考" aria-hidden="true"></a></h1><ol>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudjJleC5jb20vYW1wL3QvMzQ3MTc2LzM=" title="https://www.v2ex.com/amp/t/347176/3">用 Hexo 做个人 Wiki 知识管理系统<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
